data.description: Imagine living within walking distance to Ferdinand's beautiful 18th St Park, walking trails, library, YMCA, Forest Park schools and more in this immaculate 3 bedroom, 2 bath home. Located at the end of a quiet street, this hilltop property has fabulous views of the rolling hills southern Indiana has to offer. The upper level features an open floor plan eat-in kitchen creating a perfect space for everyday gatherings and entertaining, dining and living areas with access to the large covered back patio and manicured backyard. The lower level is dedicated to privacy with a separate living space equipped with a fireplace and wet bar, another full bathroom, laundry area and heated garage. This is a great opportunity in a great location in Ferdinand that you don't see often
